learning_outcomes.en:
The student will: 

understand the central ideas and concepts of J. v. Uexküll, J. Lotman and other scholars of Tartu semiotics; 

relate these ideas with their further developments and interpret them contextually; 

describe and analyse the application of the ideas and their changes; 

comprehend the impact of these thinkers on the development of semiotic theory 

acquire skills of academic discussion and group work.
